<%# 기능 소개 섹션: 3단 카드 (memoir "무엇을 하나요?" 패턴) %>
<section class="py-24 px-5" data-controller="scroll-animation">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    <%= render "shared/section_label", text: "WHAT'S TEOVIBE" %>
    <h2 class="text-subheading md:text-display font-black leading-tight mb-16" style="letter-spacing: -0.8px;">
      <%= section.title %>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <% section.section_cards.ordered.each_with_index do |card, i| %>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-card p-8" data-controller="scroll-animation">
          <% if card.icon.present? %>
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4"><%= card.icon %></div>
          <% end %>
          <h3 class="text-subheading font-extrabold mb-3"><%= card.title %></h3>
          <p class="text-base text-tv-gray leading-relaxed"><%= card.description %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
